WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
MkvDrama.net

00:00:29.446 --> 00:00:33.116
(Throughout the long night,
everything was shrouded in darkness.)

00:00:36.953 --> 00:00:40.290
(I waited for you to break through.)

00:01:19.204 --> 00:01:26.169
=Never Forget Your Enemy=

00:01:27.128 --> 00:01:32.592
=Episode 8=
(Dawn Sky)

00:01:35.011 --> 00:01:36.596
(If I could turn back time...)

00:02:14.418 --> 00:02:16.169
(I like you.)

00:02:35.029 --> 00:02:36.239
I believe it now.

00:02:37.115 --> 00:02:37.699
Believe what?

00:02:38.032 --> 00:02:39.576
This is fate.

00:02:39.909 --> 00:02:42.245
A match made in heaven,

00:02:42.584 --> 00:02:45.344
growing old together till your hair
turns gray... Something like that?

00:02:45.540 --> 00:02:46.583
Stop teasing.

00:02:47.500 --> 00:02:48.293
Why?

00:02:48.580 --> 00:02:50.580
You're basically
the official couple of our school.

00:02:51.513 --> 00:02:53.515
You guys don't even need to draw seats.

00:02:54.174 --> 00:02:56.384
You're partners all year anyway.

00:02:56.509 --> 00:02:58.845
I mean, all you did was switch seats.

00:02:58.845 --> 00:03:01.024
What is this, like a married couple
moving in together?

00:03:01.024 --> 00:03:01.681
Hey.

00:03:01.973 --> 00:03:02.640
Let's move.

00:03:09.314 --> 00:03:10.315
Stop teasing.

00:03:26.206 --> 00:03:27.207
Hi? Saebyeok.

00:03:29.542 --> 00:03:30.585
Hey, Saebyeok...

00:03:32.915 --> 00:03:34.208
I like you.

00:03:34.756 --> 00:03:36.466
I've liked you for a long time.

00:03:38.024 --> 00:03:38.733
So?

00:03:47.290 --> 00:03:51.360
(Gi Haneul)

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:02.720
What about mine?

00:04:17.641 --> 00:04:20.603
(I should've said that sooner.)

00:04:35.360 --> 00:04:36.317
You should be careful.

00:05:01.968 --> 00:05:02.927
Hey, Gi Haneul.

00:05:11.994 --> 00:05:13.496
Why are you so cocky lately?

00:05:16.544 --> 00:05:18.944
Because you're good at tennis,
you don't see me as a senior?

00:05:19.552 --> 00:05:20.361
No, that's not it.

00:05:22.196 --> 00:05:22.864
Not it?

00:05:24.291 --> 00:05:27.253
Oh, so you covered my mistake
on purpose in today's match.

00:05:28.077 --> 00:05:29.120
Even as a junior,

00:05:29.620 --> 00:05:31.080
thanks for saving

00:05:31.289 --> 00:05:32.457
your senior's pride.

00:05:35.001 --> 00:05:35.585
Hey.

00:05:36.127 --> 00:05:37.337
If you're that good,

00:05:38.796 --> 00:05:39.964
you should be the ace.

00:05:41.215 --> 00:05:42.425
I'll give you my spot.

00:05:42.925 --> 00:05:44.052
That's not it.

00:05:49.182 --> 00:05:50.308
If that's not it,

00:05:54.062 --> 00:05:54.896
then just play

00:05:55.772 --> 00:05:56.647
better.

00:05:57.732 --> 00:05:58.399
Junior.

00:06:15.264 --> 00:06:16.224
Hey, what's your deal?

00:06:16.584 --> 00:06:17.335
What's yours?

00:06:21.974 --> 00:06:23.000
(Yeo Saebyeok)
First year?

00:06:24.258 --> 00:06:25.301
You want to die?

00:06:25.510 --> 00:06:28.471
Instead of blaming others
for your lack of skill, practice more.

00:06:29.514 --> 00:06:30.880
Or if you really can't make it,

00:06:31.057 --> 00:06:32.392
just quit tennis.

00:06:33.393 --> 00:06:34.644
Are you done talking, you punk?

00:06:38.106 --> 00:06:39.065
Oh, you're the one, huh?

00:06:40.768 --> 00:06:41.734
Gi Haneul's boyfriend?

00:06:46.489 --> 00:06:47.448
Cut it out.

00:06:49.492 --> 00:06:50.535
Unless you want to die.

00:07:02.432 --> 00:07:04.832
- What did you do in math class today?
- I slept.

00:07:06.926 --> 00:07:07.510
Gi Haneul.

00:07:09.637 --> 00:07:10.221
Let's go.

00:07:14.559 --> 00:07:15.476
I'll go ahead.

00:07:15.552 --> 00:07:16.352
See you tomorrow.

00:07:18.521 --> 00:07:20.148
Saebyeok is handsome.

00:07:25.080 --> 00:07:27.999
(I like you too.)

00:07:30.324 --> 00:07:33.286
Grand Slam.

00:07:38.499 --> 00:07:40.501
National team.

00:07:41.169 --> 00:07:44.130
Gold medal.

00:07:48.200 --> 00:07:49.800
Don't you have anything you want to do?

00:07:50.178 --> 00:07:50.887
I do.

00:07:51.584 --> 00:07:52.832
Why aren't you writing it down?

00:07:53.400 --> 00:07:55.240
They said to do it during break
and hand it in.

00:07:57.310 --> 00:07:58.269
Because it's a secret.

00:08:00.521 --> 00:08:01.355
What are you saying?

00:08:02.315 --> 00:08:02.982
Class president!

00:08:03.700 --> 00:08:04.200
Here.

00:08:16.314 --> 00:08:21.050
(Career Aspiration Form,
Career Aspiration: Choi Soojong)

00:08:33.888 --> 00:08:36.098
(In the end, we...)

00:08:36.815 --> 00:08:39.776
(couldn't become anything.)

00:08:56.613 --> 00:08:57.877
Gi Haneul!

00:09:37.754 --> 00:09:38.528
(Recent Calls)

00:09:38.528 --> 00:09:39.456
(Haneul)

00:09:44.096 --> 00:09:46.240
The number you have dialed
is currently switched off.

00:09:46.240 --> 00:09:47.744
Please try again after the beep...

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:52.672
Who is it? Saebyeok?

00:09:56.887 --> 00:09:57.847
Oh, Saebyeok.

00:09:58.055 --> 00:09:59.849
What's going on at this hour?

00:10:00.558 --> 00:10:01.726
Where is Haneul?

00:10:01.809 --> 00:10:02.685
Haneul?

00:10:03.603 --> 00:10:04.895
He didn't come home today.

00:10:05.062 --> 00:10:05.646
What's wrong?

00:10:05.646 --> 00:10:06.355
Haneul...

00:10:06.856 --> 00:10:07.857
Haneul is missing.

00:10:08.399 --> 00:10:09.191
What?

00:10:16.896 --> 00:10:18.112
You finally picked up.

00:10:18.112 --> 00:10:20.224
The hit-and-run driver
turned himself in during the day.

00:10:20.224 --> 00:10:22.063
So Gi Haneul
also went to the police station.

00:10:22.063 --> 00:10:23.778
Haneul met the hit-and-run driver?

00:10:24.000 --> 00:10:24.500
Yes.

00:10:24.832 --> 00:10:26.125
Didn't Gi Haneul tell you?

00:10:26.834 --> 00:10:29.086
They used to work together at a cafe.

00:10:29.086 --> 00:10:29.587
What?

00:10:30.588 --> 00:10:31.213
Who?

00:10:31.505 --> 00:10:32.715
Han Jeongyun.

00:10:33.007 --> 00:10:34.759
I heard he used that alias.

00:10:35.468 --> 00:10:37.011
Yoo... Yoon Junghan?

00:10:38.179 --> 00:10:39.180
Yoon Junghan?

00:10:41.223 --> 00:10:43.184
What time did Haneul leave the station?

00:10:43.601 --> 00:10:44.894
Around seven in the evening?

00:10:48.481 --> 00:10:49.565
Haneul is missing.

00:10:50.040 --> 00:10:50.540
What?

00:10:54.195 --> 00:10:56.364
(I was wondering if Yoon Junghan
might be behind it.)

00:10:57.907 --> 00:10:59.519
(Could there be accomplices?)

00:11:01.118 --> 00:11:02.953
(There might be a possibility.)

00:11:03.493 --> 00:11:06.121
(But it's not something
we can confirm right now.)

00:11:18.803 --> 00:11:22.181
(The murderer is you, Gi Haneul.)

00:11:24.323 --> 00:11:25.199
(Please...)

00:11:30.336 --> 00:11:31.840
Darn it!

00:11:52.253 --> 00:11:55.423
(Haneul)

00:12:03.712 --> 00:12:05.792
The number you have dialed
is currently switched off.

00:12:05.792 --> 00:12:07.287
Please try again after the beep...

00:12:21.143 --> 00:12:22.853
(Thinking of)

00:12:23.342 --> 00:12:24.260
(our memories,)

00:12:24.952 --> 00:12:26.996
(I set out aimlessly.)

00:12:28.527 --> 00:12:30.852
(I absolutely won't break up with you.)

00:12:48.017 --> 00:12:48.934
(Haneul.)

00:12:50.880 --> 00:12:51.395
Hmm?

00:12:53.230 --> 00:12:56.650
I wish everything about you
could be my fault.

00:12:58.282 --> 00:12:59.989
So you'd never blame yourself.

00:13:01.739 --> 00:13:03.324
I just want you to be happy, Haneul.

00:13:07.401 --> 00:13:08.352
Let's do it together.

00:13:10.856 --> 00:13:11.690
(Let's be happy)

00:13:12.245 --> 00:13:13.288
(together.)

00:14:11.058 --> 00:14:12.017
Any updates?

00:14:12.187 --> 00:14:16.167
Gi Haneul's mother already
withdrew the missing person report.

00:14:16.256 --> 00:14:16.768
What?

00:14:17.768 --> 00:14:18.477
His mother?

00:14:28.096 --> 00:14:29.889
(Where is Haneul?)

00:14:34.748 --> 00:14:35.541
Saebyeok.

00:14:36.292 --> 00:14:36.917
Ma'am.

00:14:38.127 --> 00:14:39.044
Please tell me.

00:14:43.257 --> 00:14:45.050
I don't know where he is either.

00:14:46.416 --> 00:14:47.084
He just

00:14:47.678 --> 00:14:48.721
asked us to wait.

00:14:49.555 --> 00:14:50.306
Please.

00:14:52.266 --> 00:14:54.226
That's all I know.

00:14:57.396 --> 00:14:58.647
I'm dying.

00:15:03.412 --> 00:15:04.121
Saebyeok.

00:15:04.778 --> 00:15:05.613
Look at me.

00:15:08.532 --> 00:15:11.952
Let's give Haneul some time, huh?

00:15:14.705 --> 00:15:15.623
No.

00:15:19.960 --> 00:15:23.505
Haneul is just keeping his distance
to hold himself together.

00:15:26.258 --> 00:15:27.551
What if he never comes back?

00:15:28.093 --> 00:15:28.802
He will.

00:15:30.554 --> 00:15:31.931
He's just a little shaken

00:15:32.514 --> 00:15:34.058
and lost his way for a moment.

00:15:35.167 --> 00:15:37.253
He'll definitely come back
when time passes.

00:15:48.197 --> 00:15:51.158
I'm sorry, but my son
comes first, Saebyeok.

00:16:44.753 --> 00:16:48.799
(Gi Haneul, it should
have been you who died)

00:16:48.799 --> 00:16:49.591
Gi Haneul.

00:16:51.719 --> 00:16:53.220
It should have been you who died.

00:17:08.277 --> 00:17:12.114
(Everything will end
if only you disappear)

00:17:13.814 --> 00:17:16.984
Everything will end
if only you disappear.

00:17:30.680 --> 00:17:32.098
I pray every day

00:17:33.404 --> 00:17:36.366
(I pray every day that you'll be miserable)
that you'll be miserable.

00:17:55.195 --> 00:17:56.363
(That was)

00:17:57.046 --> 00:17:58.256
(never your place anyway.)

00:18:00.755 --> 00:18:01.590
That was never

00:18:04.667 --> 00:18:05.460
your place anyway.

00:18:09.880 --> 00:18:10.631
Saebyeok.

00:18:13.092 --> 00:18:14.802
Are you really not
going to eat anything?

00:18:15.843 --> 00:18:17.678
You'll collapse if you keep this up.

00:18:19.014 --> 00:18:20.103
It's been a month already.

00:19:03.058 --> 00:19:07.286
(Meanwhile, actor Yeo Saebyeok
is raising fans' expectations)

00:19:07.312 --> 00:19:09.565
(with his increasingly
striking appearance on set.)

00:19:10.357 --> 00:19:13.027
(Actor Yeo Saebyeok
gets more amazing by the day.)

00:19:13.028 --> 00:19:15.696
(We'd love to have him
as a guest sometime!)

00:19:22.213 --> 00:19:25.676
Seriously, this isn't just a day or two.
Isn't this too much?

00:19:26.367 --> 00:19:27.106
I'm sorry.

00:19:27.732 --> 00:19:30.151
Recently, Saebyeok hasn't been well

00:19:30.531 --> 00:19:31.931
and has been going to the hospital.

00:19:31.977 --> 00:19:37.489
We know. But if you'd given us some notice,
we could have adjusted the schedule.

00:19:38.051 --> 00:19:41.013
Do you know how much production cost
is lost in a day like this?

00:19:41.555 --> 00:19:43.098
(Haneul)
I know. I'm sorry.

00:19:43.765 --> 00:19:46.226
I'll make sure this never happens again.

00:19:47.697 --> 00:19:48.824
Please,

00:19:49.271 --> 00:19:50.689
things are already tough.

00:19:51.064 --> 00:19:52.399
Let's work well together.

00:20:02.225 --> 00:20:05.979
(Sunny days are expected ahead.
This has been the weather report!)

00:20:07.338 --> 00:20:08.768
(Actor Yeo Saebyeok Found Collapsed at Home)
(Next news.)

00:20:08.768 --> 00:20:12.457
(Popular actor Yeo Saebyeok
was found collapsed at home)

00:20:12.510 --> 00:20:14.688
(and was rushed to a nearby hospital.)

00:20:14.688 --> 00:20:17.920
(His exact condition and the circumstances
are currently under investigation.)

00:20:18.383 --> 00:20:19.134
Yeo Saebyeok.

00:20:20.507 --> 00:20:21.326
No!

00:20:31.939 --> 00:20:34.900
(People often fail
to see their own light.)

00:20:35.651 --> 00:20:36.568
But, I've been

00:20:37.031 --> 00:20:38.559
watching your light for a long time.

00:20:39.500 --> 00:20:40.660
From closer than anyone else.

00:20:42.829 --> 00:20:43.836
I'll tell you everything.

00:20:47.746 --> 00:20:48.580
(Yeo Saebyeok.)

00:20:50.249 --> 00:20:52.000
My amnesia.

00:20:53.673 --> 00:20:55.425
What if I never become

00:20:57.814 --> 00:20:58.857
the old me again?

00:21:00.169 --> 00:21:01.337
It's okay.

00:21:03.242 --> 00:21:03.910
I

00:21:04.557 --> 00:21:05.808
won't give up on you.

00:21:09.493 --> 00:21:10.577
This is...

00:21:11.190 --> 00:21:13.710
I always thought
you'd play tennis again.

00:21:14.336 --> 00:21:15.809
Don't worry about anything.

00:21:16.032 --> 00:21:17.178
Just think about yourself.

00:21:25.534 --> 00:21:29.162
(504, Yeo Saebyeok)

00:22:05.609 --> 00:22:06.610
I missed you.

00:22:12.173 --> 00:22:12.924
I've been waiting.

00:23:03.232 --> 00:23:04.432
(The sentence is as follows.)

00:23:04.811 --> 00:23:11.382
(For defendant, Han Jeongyun, 7 years in prison,
and for defendant, Lee Seri, life imprisonment.)

00:23:26.178 --> 00:23:27.715
Pull it tighter over there.

00:23:27.776 --> 00:23:28.770
I'm pulling it.

00:23:29.114 --> 00:23:30.216
Now, tuck it underneath.

00:23:31.445 --> 00:23:32.738
- Did you tuck it underneath?
- Hmm.

00:23:32.738 --> 00:23:33.238
I tucked it.

00:23:35.752 --> 00:23:37.203
Okay, the blanket.

00:23:39.227 --> 00:23:40.289
Hold it.

00:23:43.610 --> 00:23:44.278
- Here I go.
- Yeah.

00:23:44.556 --> 00:23:46.016
One, two, three.

00:23:54.345 --> 00:23:55.137
Done.

00:24:03.275 --> 00:24:05.110
Seriously, what are you doing?

00:24:52.032 --> 00:24:52.616
I love you.

00:24:55.631 --> 00:24:56.465
I love you.

00:27:28.256 --> 00:27:29.159
I love you.

00:27:31.520 --> 00:27:32.155
I love you.

00:28:36.965 --> 00:28:37.549
I'm

00:28:38.258 --> 00:28:39.426
thinking of quitting acting.

00:28:41.376 --> 00:28:41.876
What?

00:28:43.488 --> 00:28:43.988
Why?

00:28:46.102 --> 00:28:46.936
My future dream.

00:28:48.935 --> 00:28:49.728
What is it?

00:28:51.938 --> 00:28:52.522
It's a secret.

00:28:53.719 --> 00:28:54.553
Ah, what is it?

00:28:54.775 --> 00:28:55.567
Tell me.

00:29:03.324 --> 00:29:04.909
After I lost my memory,

00:29:05.160 --> 00:29:06.286
when we came here,

00:29:06.995 --> 00:29:08.247
I asked you, remember?

00:29:10.178 --> 00:29:11.304
"What is this place?"

00:29:14.510 --> 00:29:15.302
Did you remember?

00:29:17.922 --> 00:29:18.423
Hmm.

00:29:21.554 --> 00:29:22.138
Tell me.

00:29:42.071 --> 00:29:42.655
Our...

00:29:44.491 --> 00:29:45.033
first kiss.

00:29:58.881 --> 00:30:00.507
(Hello, I'm an actor, Yeo Saebyeok.)

00:30:02.208 --> 00:30:03.972
(Actress Yeo Saebyeok Press Conference)
The time I've lived as an actor

00:30:03.973 --> 00:30:06.346
(Will quietly walk a new path)
has been like a beautiful season in my life.

00:30:06.679 --> 00:30:10.391
But now, I feel another path
calling me from within.

00:30:11.601 --> 00:30:15.730
It feels like it's time to fully live
my own life, not just as a character.

00:30:16.606 --> 00:30:19.692
Not as a character in a work,
but as the main character of my own life.

00:30:20.134 --> 00:30:23.679
I want to spend my remaining time
more meaningfully.

00:30:24.577 --> 00:30:26.745
I sincerely thank everyone

00:30:27.142 --> 00:30:28.811
who has stood by me.

00:30:30.411 --> 00:30:31.996
I hope you all continue to live

00:30:32.288 --> 00:30:34.165
shining lives in your own places.

00:30:34.999 --> 00:30:37.578
I will also quietly walk my own path.

00:30:38.336 --> 00:30:39.170
Thank you.

00:30:42.882 --> 00:30:47.512
(Top star Yeo Saebyeok announced
his retirement at today's press conference.)

00:30:48.471 --> 00:30:51.616
(Having left behind numerous hit works,)

00:30:51.616 --> 00:30:54.516
(Yeo Saebyeok became a representative actor
of the Korean film industry.)

00:30:55.411 --> 00:30:58.871
(He plans to finish
his already scheduled projects)

00:30:58.871 --> 00:31:02.055
(before ending his acting career.)

00:31:03.302 --> 00:31:06.974
(Fans are disappointed
by the sudden news,)

00:31:06.975 --> 00:31:12.829
(but they're also sending warm messages
of support for Yeo Saebyeok's new chapter.)

00:31:15.085 --> 00:31:17.857
(In particular,
his final work before retirement,)

00:31:17.858 --> 00:31:22.463
(the film "Never Forget Your Enemy",
is scheduled for release this February.)

00:31:39.066 --> 00:31:42.820
(And so, may you dispel my darkness)

00:31:43.234 --> 00:31:45.945
(and fill it with new light.)

00:31:46.195 --> 00:31:46.905
(Just as)

00:31:47.447 --> 00:31:48.990
(the dawn always does.)

00:32:14.394 --> 00:32:17.984
(You become my new beginning every day.)

00:32:41.882 --> 00:32:44.919
♪The more I try to run away♪

00:32:45.217 --> 00:32:46.900
♪The clearer it becomes♪

00:32:48.502 --> 00:32:51.792
♪Even the word "love"♪

00:32:52.088 --> 00:32:53.279
♪Can't convey how I feel♪

00:32:55.348 --> 00:32:58.421
♪Watching your shadow moving forward♪

00:32:58.650 --> 00:33:00.282
♪Sometimes, I resent you♪

00:33:00.282 --> 00:33:02.144
♪But without you,
everything feels strange♪

00:33:02.373 --> 00:33:07.443
♪The pain also makes me grow♪

00:33:08.890 --> 00:33:10.790
♪There is a lot to say♪

00:33:10.790 --> 00:33:12.210
♪Trying to separate us♪

00:33:12.523 --> 00:33:15.368
♪Even if I look like a fool♪

00:33:15.964 --> 00:33:17.484
♪It doesn't matter♪

00:33:17.484 --> 00:33:19.450
♪This is how we are♪

00:33:19.450 --> 00:33:22.365
♪Connected to each other♪

00:33:22.426 --> 00:33:25.945
♪We are truly strange♪

00:33:26.426 --> 00:33:29.477
♪Pushing each other away,
yet embracing again♪

00:33:29.477 --> 00:33:31.770
♪Between love and pain♪

00:33:31.802 --> 00:33:34.813
♪In some corner♪

00:33:34.964 --> 00:33:38.449
♪In the end, we can only be together♪

00:33:45.556 --> 00:33:49.388
♪Because that's us♪

00:33:52.842 --> 00:33:54.202
♪Even if what we said yesterday♪

00:33:54.202 --> 00:33:55.656
♪Remains in the heart♪

00:33:55.834 --> 00:33:57.626
♪As time passes♪

00:33:57.626 --> 00:33:58.842
♪Maybe I'll laugh about it♪

00:33:58.842 --> 00:34:00.922
♪Even those painful memories♪

00:34:00.922 --> 00:34:02.042
♪Are also ours♪

00:34:02.196 --> 00:34:04.776
♪Seems we can♪

00:34:04.776 --> 00:34:06.713
♪Be more understanding♪

00:34:07.188 --> 00:34:09.372
♪I clearly told myself♪

00:34:10.394 --> 00:34:12.652
♪Never to see you again♪

00:34:12.890 --> 00:34:15.599
♪But hearing your voice♪

00:34:15.956 --> 00:34:16.986
♪I completely break down♪

